Link":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result.addExtraArgs","kind":"def","line":919,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Result.addExtraArgs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L919-L926"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.tryAutoCongrTheorem?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">tryAutoCongrTheorem?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.SimpM\">SimpM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Try to use automatically generated congruence theorems. See `mkCongrSimp?`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.tryAutoCongrTheorem?","kind":"def","line":804,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.tryAutoCongrTheorem?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L804-L917"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.mkCongrSimp?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkCongrSimp?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.SimpM\">SimpM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/CongrTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.CongrTheorem\">CongrTheorem</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Retrieve auto-generated congruence lemma for `f`.\n\nRemark: If all argument kinds are `fixed` or `eq`, it returns `none` because\nusing simple congruence theorems `congr`, `congrArg`, and `congrFun` produces a more compact proof.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.mkCongrSimp?","kind":"def","line":767,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.mkCongrSimp?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L767-L801"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.simpAppUsingCongr\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">simpAppUsingCongr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.SimpM\">SimpM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given an application `e`, recursively simplifies its function and arguments and constructs a proof\nusing `congrArg`, `congrFun`, `congrFun'` and `congr`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.simpAppUsingCongr","kind":"def","line":728,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.simpAppUsingCongr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L728-L765"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.congrArgs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">congrArgs</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">args</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.SimpM\">SimpM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a simplified function result `r` and arguments `args`, simplify arguments using `simp` and `dsimp`.\nThe resulting proof is built using `congr` and `congrFun` theorems.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.congrArgs","kind":"def","line":645,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.congrArgs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L645-L679"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.removeUnnecessaryCasts\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">removeUnnecessaryCasts</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span c