M</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.mkEqTransResultStep","kind":"def","line":359,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.mkEqTransResultStep","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L359-L364"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.TransformStep.toStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">TransformStep</span>.<span class=\"name\">toStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Transform.html#Lean.TransformStep\">TransformStep</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Meta.Simp.Step</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.TransformStep.toStep","kind":"def","line":352,"name":"Lean.TransformStep.toStep","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L352-L357"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DSimproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Similar to `Simproc`, but resulting expression should be definitionally equal to the input one.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc","kind":"def","line":347,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.DSimproc","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L347-L350"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep","kind":"def","line":345,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.DStep","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L345-L345"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A simplification procedure. Recall that we have `pre` and `post` procedures.\nSee `Step`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc","kind":"def","line":339,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L339-L343"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedStep</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep","kind":"instance","line":337,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedStep","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L337-L337"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">continue</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e?</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a></span> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option.none\">none</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For `pre` procedures, continue transformation by visiting subexpressions, and then\nexecuting `post` procedures.\n\nFor `post` procedures, this is equivalent to returning `visit`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue","kind":"ctor","line":330,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.continue","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L330-L336"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">visit</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For `pre` procedures, the resulting expression is passed to `pre` again.\n\nFor `post` procedures, the resulting expression is passed to `pre` again IF\n`Simp.Config.singlePass := false` and resulting expression is not equal to initial expression.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit","kind":"ctor","line":323,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.visit","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L323-L329"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">done</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Result\">Result</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\">Step</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For `pre` procedures, it returns the result without visiting any subexpressions.\n\nFor `post` procedures, it returns the result.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done","kind":"ctor","line":317,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step.done","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L317-L322"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Result type for a simplification procedure. We have `pre` and `post` simplification procedures.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Step","kind":"inductive","line":313,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Step","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L313-L337"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.modifyDiag\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">modifyDiag</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Diagnostics\">Diagnostics</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Diagnostics\">Diagnostics</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lea