pan>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedContext</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Context</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedContext","kind":"instance","line":123,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.instInhabitedContext","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L123-L123"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.inDSimp\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">inDSimp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `inDSimp := true`, then `simp` is in `dsimp` mode, and only applying\ntransformations that preserve definitional equality.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.inDSimp","kind":"def","line":122,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.inDSimp","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L122-L122"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.lctxInitIndices\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">lctxInitIndices</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Number of indices in the local context when starting `simp`.\nWe use this information to decide which assumptions we can use without\ninvalidating the cache.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.lctxInitIndices","kind":"def","line":117,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.lctxInitIndices","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L117-L117"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.dischargeDepth\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">dischargeDepth</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt32\">UInt32</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.dischargeDepth","kind":"def","line":111,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.dischargeDepth","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.lean#L111-L111"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.parent?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Context</span>.<span class=\"name\">parent?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context\">Context</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Stores the \"parent\" term for the term being simplified.\nIf a simplification procedure result depends on this value,\nthen it is its responsibility to set `Result.cache := false`.\n\nMotivation for this field:\nSuppose we have a simplification procedure for normalizing arithmetic terms.\nThen, given a term such as `t_1 + ... + t_n`, we don't want to apply the procedure\nto every subterm `t_1 + ... + t_i` for `i < n` for performance issues. The procedure\ncan accomplish this by checking whether the parent term is also an arithmetical expression\nand do nothing if it is. However, it should set `Result.cache := false` to ensure\nwe don't miss simplification opportunities. For example, consider the following:\n```\nexample (x y : Nat) (h : y = 0) : id ((x + x) + y) = id (x + x) := by\n  simp +arith only\n  ...\n```\nIf we don't set `Result.cache := false` for the first `x + x`, then we get\nthe resulting state:\n```\n... |- id (2*x + y) = id (x + x)\n```\ninstead of\n```\n... |- id (2*x + y) = id (2*x)\n```\nas expected.\n\nRemark: given an application `f a b c` the \"parent\" term for `f`, `a`, `b`, and `c`\nis `f a b c`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.parent?","kind":"def","line":110,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.Context.parent?"